data.description: Charming 3bedroom 2bathroom home in Barretts Trace Subdivision. This well maintained home has an updated kitchen and all of the appliances except the refrigerator will remain. 2 car garage with updated flooring. HVAC and water heater 1 year old. Covered front porch and fenced back yard. This home is conveniently located to shopping, dining, recreation and the interstate. Schedule your showing today and make an offer.
